d3bbaec","tid":482610,"uid":144774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T13:42:14.000Z","msg":"會唔會中過六合彩咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf9bdda46f4329947c908887cdc622843e6f57f","tid":482610,"uid":113966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T13:52:16.000Z","msg":"父母五十歲 都無五十個呀<br />\n550萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0abca5a938c5fec7ea29f37288cc774a1e085c8e","tid":482610,"uid":14162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T14:01:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171128/large/1511862144_8e59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171128%2Flarge%2F1511862144_8e59.jpg&h=d3c7ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171128/large/1511856494_5c34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171128%2Flarge%2F1511856494_5c34.jpg&h=fe8464d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消息指，沙田第一城6座中層D室，實用面積853方呎，屬屋苑面積最大間隔，三房連主人套房設計，另設工人房，單位昨以1,095萬元易手，呎價12,837元，終升破2016年9月錄得的1,080萬元（連天台特色戶）高位，成沙田第一城歷來最貴樓王。單位今年9月放盤，叫價1,200萬元，屬罕有交吉鎖匙盤。<br />\n<br />\n新買家為一名25歲青年，由母親資助一半首期近550萬元入市。代理透露，這位廿四孝好媽媽，年約50餘歲，任職清潔，月入約1.5萬元，丈夫就做維修，兩公婆多年來死慳死抵，儲到一舊錢，兒子就快結婚，[red]所以父母就把部份積蓄［/red]幫助兒子買樓。父母本身在沙田區已有兩層樓，一層自住，一層收租。新購的沙田第一城樓王就會一齊住。<br />\n<br />\n對於市場瘋傳，今次易手的第一城樓王，同時獲三客爭購，新買家更代地產代理支付佣金。消息指，「三個客爭就真，買家代畀佣就梗係假啦!」。<br />\n本報取得該樓王內櫳相片，客廳巨大，附設的露台享有開揚城門河景。<br />\n原業主1997年5月以605萬元買入單位，持貨20年升值八成，賬面獲利490萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171128/57515558\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171128%2F57515558&d=%2BUhygSBzZLCudYLKhSgcVBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=07e14d63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171128%2F57515558&h=0a53d933\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171128/57515558</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ab2a9b3e3c465828c9b95da08137fa5e27535970","tid":482610,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T14:12:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做清潔1.5萬咁好搵?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n洗足8個鐘 辛苦錢黎架<br />\n酒樓洗碗有萬八tim</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n酒樓仲要一早去返工 中午落場 夜晚再返<br />\n成日咁就冇左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b1bcc521213c13d8f157101d2903b1093d7993","tid":482610,"uid":120955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T14:20:32.000Z","msg":"包租婆先係正職<br />\n清潔係兼職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc5978a486667c2cf09c1f61ad485601b90edb0","tid":482610,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T14:27:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完淨係想講：他媽的！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢就慘了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fade6f90ce8202bfb3316c5dd551f665b8b802c","tid":482610,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T14:39:43.000Z","msg":"關鍵詞<br />\n一齊住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb55cbaf7a916cf67daa6a4d8cbe903e7ddf9cb","tid":482610,"uid":19776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T14:57:25.000Z","msg":"我公司有個清潔呀姐又係係沙田有兩層樓<br />\n唔知係咪講緊佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f381c48d5a329fd9c7038947d2fd73a924bd109","tid":482610,"uid":87254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T15:29:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一千個 買咁舊嘅樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你以為一千萬三房有好多選擇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca994fd18c937ff869e2480e34050e27db492b02","tid":482610,"uid":88029,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T15:41:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0155c27bdfd94b74896044f684dc8b1ffe36dc5","tid":482610,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T15:46:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67aaa560b9c81f9b09b063348f35e440d0a99500","tid":482610,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T15:51:57.000Z","msg":"上一代真係儲錢王.<br />\n<br />\n有個客男既做地盤雜工, 女既做清潔, 又係買三百萬樓另加四十萬裝修.<br />\n<br />\n我老豆份糧萬五, 養四條友又可以儲二百萬加大陸兩間屋.<br />\n<br />\n我一個人萬五絕對唔夠洗但明明已經好慳個隻,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢班人死晒樓價搵鬼買, D人連首期中既首期都未必俾得起."},{"pid":"8c5b6767f1459658adfe8b7bb855328d8cc61e6f","tid":482610,"uid":49497,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T16:06:35.000Z","msg":"15000人工一蚊都唔洗<br />\n做30年野就有540萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc946167493c93ab1718b4fe10f7682ca5224c9d","tid":482610,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T16:09:14.000Z","msg":"佢賣左住緊層居屋，拎左550萬做首期買呢個一千萬既單位，唔係點解要一齊住"},{"pid":"7e5c6a51446a25d508bd18b0dc54859e6920df33","tid":482610,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T16:13:08.000Z","msg":"1000萬樓，比左500萬，供30年，每個月先供18000，抵到爛屎忽，"},{"pid":"b816365b82d14b8f239f8b0c5c79faf6b195898b","tid":482610,"uid":120499,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T16:16:46.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得呢種人可能係支